name: Sanjay Casting & Engineering Company
head: Mr Bishnu  Kumar Kedia
about:
The Earth receives more solar energy every hour than what the world population consumes in an entire year. Solar energy is limitless, businesses and industries around the world can immensely benefit by harnessing solar technologies for tackling their energy challenges. 
 
Sanjay Casting & Engineering Company based out of Kolkata, India, works to accelerate the production and commercialization of advanced solar technologies in the form of its innovative and practical range of Solar Water Tank, Solar Panel Mounting Structures, Solar Frames, Solar Water Heater Tank, Solar Panel Structure, Module Mounting Structure, etc. Assistance is also offered for Solar Panel Installation so that clients can manage their solar system designs with complete ease. 
 
The company knows that clients decide to invest in solar energy to maximize profits and contribute their share to the well-being of the planet. Therefore, as a part of its core work policies, it holds commitments made to benefit clients with the highest regard. It also fuels its innovative practices to remain at the forefront of leading solar power technology. While it helps hundreds of industrial, commercial and residential customers reap the benefits of clean energy production through its world-class range, it also meets promised deadlines when executing installation services. 
 
Sanjay Casting & Engineering Company is not your regular solar product manufacturer and exporter but a reputable, quality-approved firm that has been in business for close to 50 years and whose impressive solutions are a cut above the rest. It has highly qualified teams of solar energy specialists, each dedicated to their craft. This passionate crew of engineers, technicians, quality analysts and researchers strive together to build tailored systems and solutions that meet the unique needs of its Indian and global clients seeking sustainable energy solutions.
 
Want to know how the company can create Solar Water Tank, Solar Panel Mounting Structure, Solar Frame, Solar Water Heater Tank, Solar Panel Structure, Module Mounting Structure, etc., as per your requirements and budget? Do not hesitate to contact the company experts waiting to serve you!
 
Leadership
 
Good leadership is fundamental to the effective functioning of any organization, and this company is no exception. However, it feels blessed to be directed by an involved leader like Mr. Bishnu Kumar Kedi (Director-Sales). He believes in standing firmly with each client in their renewable energy journey while they get to experience the latest solar technologies through the many innovative products of the company. Under his direction, each product is engineered to align with exacting international standards and sold at marginal prices to worldwide clients after being passed through a series of checks and balances to ensure their unbeatable quality and functionality.
 
As a tech leader who has a truly deep understanding of the sector and looks toward a bright future for the company, Mr. Bishnu Kumar Kedi singlehandedly works through numerous business processes with unmatchable agility, linking cutting-edge solar technology back to the core ambitions of the organization. He also knows how to work well with the key teams of the company and set it for future growth and success as a reliable manufacturer of Solar Water Tank, Solar Panel Mounting Structure, Solar Frame, Solar Water Heater Tank, Solar Panel Structure, Module Mounting Structure, etc., with his ethics, professionalism and cooperation. 
 
Why Choose Sanjay Casting & Engineering Company?
 
Since the year 1974, the company has been fully immersed in utilizing robust technologies to power its business. From recruiting and nurturing tech-savvy experts with fluency in key solar technologies to investing in the right resources that would simplify its working in a complex and global operating environment, the company does it all to stay ahead of the curve. Let us learn what makes the firm a frontrunner in a rapidly-changing global marketplace.
 

1. Experience: The company uses its rich market insights and knowledge built over many decades to stay ahead of the curve as a seller of standard and customized solar-based products.
	 
2. Quality Raw Materials: Raw materials are yardsticks through which the quality of the final output can be evaluated. The company utilizes the right mix of raw inputs like zinc, iron, pig iron, and steel to fabricate its range.
	 
3. Good Pricing: Technologically-rich Solar Water Tank, Solar Panel Mounting Structure, Solar Frame, Solar Water Heater Tank, Solar Panel Structure, Module Mounting Structure, etc., offered come with the added advantage of easy pricing. The company passes on great savings to customers based on its transparent pricing policy, whether one is bulk-buying or just placing orders for a single product.
	 
4. Quick Customization: Everything is offered as per the specific energy needs and requirements of customers. Any order requiring customization is completed as per the committed schedule too.
	 

Vision & Mission
 
The company mission is to ensure its unrivaled quality manifests itself across various processes and products. It envisions sustaining its technology leadership and creating future-ready solutions that address the solar energy needs of today and tomorrow.

Access to a whole spectrum of client opinions gives them ideas on how to cultivate better practices for enabling further business growth and boosting client satisfaction through product/process improvement. Wound Component Pvt. name: Vea Impex (I) Private Limited
head: Mr Manthan Rohit Shah
about:
Words like patient-centricity and operational resilience have become common among pharmaceutical companies these days post the Covid-19 pandemic. The threat has significantly reinforced among pharma companies the importance of staying on their toes to cater to market needs with agility and speed. No company can think of rising in the healthcare market if it resorts to passiveness or fails to meet market needs with consumer-friendliness. Therefore, growing competition can be seen among the Indian suppliers and exporters to differentiate themselves from the rest with most adopting more patient-friendly measures and supplying vital medicines and other products across multiple drug categories at competitive prices, exactly as per schedules promised. One such Indian company specialising in effective and low-cost Generic Medicines, Pharmaceutical Drugs, Anti Cancer Medicines & Injections, COVID-19 Medicine & Products, IV Fluids-Intravenous Infusion, Antiseptic and Disinfectant, etc., is Vea Impex from Mumbai, Maharashtra.
 
The company deals in multiple product types like oral solids, liquids, topical ointments, biologicals and others. All products are purchased in bulk from reputed pharma companies that hold international approvals for their production and quality testing practices. As a trader, exporter and wholesaler, the company not just associates with providers of branded medicines but also remains active at various stages of the value chain to best serve its network of worldwide customers. Its established office in Mumbai is spacious enough and integrates multiple departments specializing in drug procurement, testing, approval, packaging and dispatch.
 
Since the time the company delivered its first batch of medicines to its very first customer in 2009, it has been honouring values like client centricity, business integrity, fairness and professionalism for forging healthy business relations and staying on track in business. From leveraging diverse experiences of its professionals to well adhering to legal and regulatory requirements, the company has been doing everything possible as a licensed seller of Generic Medicines, Pharmaceutical Drugs, Anti Cancer Medicines & Injections, COVID-19 Medicine & Products, IV Fluids-Intravenous Infusion, Antiseptic and Disinfectant, etc. It intends to carry on with the same spirit to make huge inroads into the global pharma market.
 
Today, the company has attained a level of excellence in the pharma trading and export field like no other Indian company. Its quality assured product range and outstanding service support have led to its glorious market profile. At all times it grows its business knowledge, trains its employees to very high standards and maintains ongoing interaction with customers to sustain its spot as a preferred supplier and wholesaler of Generic Medicines, Surgical Products, Veterinary Products and Medicines and other supplies. Want to experience the product reliability and service efficiency of Vea Impex? Get in touch with a company expert to join its expanding network of clients today!
 
Leadership
 
Cooperation overrides competition, which is well understood by competent leaders in business. Cooperation does not necessarily mean collaborating with a competing organization but also forging strong networks among employees within an organisation for bolstering its work performance and efficiency. Meaningful partnerships at the workplace where all employees feel equally valued, appreciated and supported leads to their contributing a fair share towards forging meaningful partnerships with clients. Therefore, Mr. Manthan Rohit Shah who leads the team at Vea Impex well illustrates the importance of collaboration and fair team play at all times. He adopts a strategic foresight to honestly evaluate the individual skills of each employee, and pave the way for their combined success and the success of each client.
 
Why Choose Vea Impex?
 

1. Vendors: The company and its vendors supplying Generic Medicines, Pharmaceutical Drugs, Anti Cancer Medicines & Injections, COVID-19 Medicine & Products, IV Fluids-Intravenous Infusion, Antiseptic and Disinfectant, etc., remain fully aligned with one another and work effectively adopting the best work procedures for the greater welfare of clients.
	 
2. Team: The company segregates professionals into different teams, each harnessing individual strengths to best contribute towards the profits of clients and the prosperity of the company. People from diverse professional and cultural backgrounds stay on the same page when working cohesively to meet specific client needs as per their expectations. 
	 
3. Price & Delivery: While operations related to procurement and packaging are done in strong agreement with global quality practices, the company remains equally enthusiastic about making deliveries across borders with unmatchable speed. It overrides complex transportation challenges of any kind & scale, quickly delivering competitively-priced products throughout the world from its base in Mumbai, India.
	 

Vision & Mission
 
The firm capitalizing on its considerable trade and export knowledge aims to grow responsibly in the global market of Generic Medicines, Pharmaceutical Drugs, Anti Cancer Medicines & Injections, COVID-19 Medicine & Products, IV Fluids-Intravenous Infusion, Antiseptic and Disinfectant, etc., also giving everyone access to a better quality of life in the process.

about:
The importance of healthcare in the society cannot be denied. Medical technology has been experiencing unprecedented progress in recent years, making the future look easier for doctors and caregivers. One can witness how the global healthcare sector has accelerated progress when it comes to dealing with deadly diseases like HIV, asthma and cancer. New breakthroughs and advancements in the field of oncology and other areas are here to help healthcare professionals and their patients experience better outcomes like never before. Making better health outcomes accessible for patients and healthcare experts across wider geographical areas is Niba Healthcare – a licensed exporter, trader and supplier of Anticancer Medicine And Injections, Oncology Drugs And Injections, Skin Care Creams And Ointments, Asthma Inhalers, Anti HIV Medicines, High Blood Pressure Drugs, Anti Acne Creams And Ointments, etc. Speedier recovery from even the most debilitating of diseases and quicker return to one’s normal life is what the company assures to the public as it works round the clock to make a difference in its field. Partnering with some of the leading vendors in the segment, it sources safe and effective medicines and drugs to promise quality of life to millions of consumers around the world on a daily basis.
 
Contact the company today to see how it has opened the door to a healthier life for so many people across the world.
 
Company Goals

- Adhering to GMP and ISO 9001:2015 standards
	 
- Finding better healthcare treatments in the market
	 
- Identifying medicine vendors with efficient delivery systems, and high-tech equipment
	 
- Giving consumers quick access to less costly branded medications like Anticancer Medicine And Injections, Oncology Drugs And Injections, Skin Care Creams And Ointments, Asthma Inhalers, Anti HIV Medicines, High Blood Pressure Drugs, Anti Acne Creams And Ointments, etc.
	 

Leadership
 
Mr Nishant Barethiya began his role as the Owner and Proprietor of Niba Healthcare in the year 2018. His aim was to collaborate with leading medicine brands and pave the path towards excellent patient care everywhere. He has faced many unique challenges but they have never deterred him from losing sight of his focus, which is to effectively tailor care for patients with severe health conditions like HIV, asthma, cancer, blood pressure and various skin diseases. His perseverance and valuable contributions have over the years helped the company achieve greatness in its field, and herald new transformations in the field of global healthcare.
 
Why Choose Niba Healthcare?
 

- Vendors: One would always find vendors who lack the will to honour quality commitments, take timely actions or remain ethically and morally grounded when dealing with partners. Thankfully, our vendors are not one of them. In fact, we can operate with agility and resilience because of our vendors, who never take shortcuts for personal gains and timely deliver us with effective and safe medicines that are formulated to treat HIV, asthma, cancer, blood pressure and various skin conditions.
	 
- Pricing: Good pricing is expected from market-leading medicine traders that have wellbeing at the core of their businesses. We too have garnered trust and respect from many consumers around the world for our fair pricing policy. We are inspired by customer contentment and sell our entire range of Anticancer Medicine And Injections, Oncology Drugs And Injections, Skin Care Creams And Ointments, Asthma Inhalers, Anti HIV Medicines, High Blood Pressure Drugs, Anti Acne Creams And Ointments, etc., at affordable prices for the convenience of our customers.
	 
- Delivery: Medicine traders need to carry out multiple works simultaneously without compromising deadlines, ever. Any inconvenience caused to a buyer because of a delayed delivery might lead to the trader losing his reputation in the industry for good. Therefore, we always dispatch orders on time and give due attention to this most important aspect of our work- delivery timing. In fact, we are known for completing small to big tasks ahead of schedules.


Vision
 
The company hopes to emerge as a talented market leader that knows how to harness its innate ability and respond to healthcare needs globally with excellence while playing on its effective trade partnerships, optimised supply chain and client-centred work strategies.

Mission
 
Our mission is to create enduring value that benefits both the company and our worldwide customers.

about:
Words like patient-centricity and operational resilience have become common among pharmaceutical companies these days post the Covid-19 pandemic. The threat has significantly reinforced among pharma companies the importance of staying on their toes to cater to market needs with agility and speed. No company can think of rising in the healthcare market if it resorts to passiveness or fails to meet market needs with consumer-friendliness. Therefore, growing competition can be seen among the Indian suppliers and exporters to differentiate themselves from the rest with most adopting more patient-friendly measures and supplying vital medicines and other products across multiple drug categories at competitive prices, exactly as per schedules promised. The company deals in multiple product types like oral solids, liquids, topical ointments, biologicals and others. All products are purchased in bulk from reputed pharma companies that hold international approvals for their production and quality testing practices. As a trader, exporter and wholesaler, the company not just associates with providers of branded medicines but also remains active at various stages of the value chain to best serve its network of worldwide customers. Its established office in Mumbai is spacious enough and integrates multiple departments specializing in drug procurement, testing, approval, packaging and dispatch.
 
Since the time the company delivered its first batch of medicines to its very first customer in 2009, it has been honouring values like client centricity, business integrity, fairness and professionalism for forging healthy business relations and staying on track in business. From leveraging diverse experiences of its professionals to well adhering to legal and regulatory requirements, the company has been doing everything possible as a licensed seller of Generic Medicines, Pharmaceutical Drugs, Anti Cancer Medicines & Injections, COVID-19 Medicine & Products, IV Fluids-Intravenous Infusion, Antiseptic and Disinfectant, etc. It intends to carry on with the same spirit to make huge inroads into the global pharma market.
 
Today, the company has attained a level of excellence in the pharma trading and export field like no other Indian company. Its quality assured product range and outstanding service support have led to its glorious market profile. At all times it grows its business knowledge, trains its employees to very high standards and maintains ongoing interaction with customers to sustain its spot as a preferred supplier and wholesaler of Generic Medicines, Surgical Products, Veterinary Products and Medicines and other supplies. Want to experience the product reliability and service efficiency of Vea Impex? Get in touch with a company expert to join its expanding network of clients today!
 
Leadership
 
Cooperation overrides competition, which is well understood by competent leaders in business. Cooperation does not necessarily mean collaborating with a competing organization but also forging strong networks among employees within an organisation for bolstering its work performance and efficiency. Meaningful partnerships at the workplace where all employees feel equally valued, appreciated and supported leads to their contributing a fair share towards forging meaningful partnerships with clients. Therefore, Mr. Manthan Rohit Shah who leads the team at Vea Impex well illustrates the importance of collaboration and fair team play at all times. He adopts a strategic foresight to honestly evaluate the individual skills of each employee, and pave the way for their combined success and the success of each client.
 
Why Choose Vea Impex?
 

1. Vendors: The company and its vendors supplying Generic Medicines, Pharmaceutical Drugs, Anti Cancer Medicines & Injections, COVID-19 Medicine & Products, IV Fluids-Intravenous Infusion, Antiseptic and Disinfectant, etc., remain fully aligned with one another and work effectively adopting the best work procedures for the greater welfare of clients.

People from diverse professional and cultural backgrounds stay on the same page when working cohesively to meet specific client needs as per their expectations. 
	 
3. Price & Delivery: While operations related to procurement and packaging are done in strong agreement with global quality practices, the company remains equally enthusiastic about making deliveries across borders with unmatchable speed. It overrides complex transportation challenges of any kind & scale, quickly delivering competitively-priced products throughout the world from its base in Mumbai, India.
	 

Vision & Mission
 
The firm capitalizing on its considerable trade and export knowledge aims to grow responsibly in the global market of Generic Medicines, Pharmaceutical Drugs, Anti Cancer Medicines & Injections, COVID-19 Medicine & Products, IV Fluids-Intravenous Infusion, Antiseptic and Disinfectant, etc., also giving everyone access to a better quality of life in the process.
